==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mangler
<hw>Man"gler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See 1st
<er>Mangle</er>.]</ety> <def>One who mangles or tears in cutting; one
who mutilates any work in doing it.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mangler</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Mangler
<hw>Man"gler</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See 3d <er>Mangle</er>.]</ety>
<def>One who smooths with a mangle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mango</ent>⟦br⟧
